headline: 1 Consumer Stock with Promising Prospects and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: Most consumer discretionary businesses succeed or fail based on the broader economy. Lately, it seems like demand trends have worked in their favor as the industry has returned 10.9% over the past six months, similar to the S&P 500.
